  "keyFeatures": [
    "Web-based UI for managing Kubernetes clusters",
    "Multi-module architecture with API, Auth, Web, and Metrics Scraper",
    "Resource management (Deployments, Pods, Services, etc.)",
    "Real-time metrics visualization",
    "Log viewing and shell access",
